      "title": "Load recipe to widgets workflow notes",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# Load Recipe To Widgets\n\n1. Fill token + asset_id/version_id on `Load Asset From GenAsset`.\n2. Queue once.\n3. `Load Recipe To Widgets` receives `workflow_json` + `metadata_json` and outputs replay values:\n   - prompt_text, negative_prompt_text, model_name\n   - seed, steps, cfg, sampler_name, scheduler, denoise\n   - width, height\n\nUse these outputs to manually copy values into sampler/prompt nodes for reproducible reruns.\n\nIf extraction is empty for some fields, that recipe did not include those keys."
      ],
